high_descs: Little bit move towards the left side to reach the counter top
Take a knife from the top of the counter
Little bit move towards the left side of the counter top
Cut the lettuce into pieces
Hold the knife and stand in front of the counter top
Put the knife behind the potato which is kept on the counter top
Reach the counter top to take the lettuce piece
Take the lettuce piece from the cut lettuce
Turn right and walk straight and turn right and take another right to reach the sink back side
Put the lettuce in the sink, wash it and take off the lettuce piece
Turn right and again take a left and once again take a left to reach the counter top
Put the lettuce on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce on the counter top

high_descs: move back in the kitchen area turn left then right move closer towards the countertop
collect the knife from the countertop
move back turn left move forward turn right towards the countertop
slice the lettuce with the knife on the countertop
move back the knife from countertop
place the knife on the countertop behind potato
move closer to the countertop
collect the sliced lettuce from the countertop
turn left go straight turn right move forward turn right move forward turn right towards the sink
put the lettuce inside the sink rinse with water collect the washed sliced lettuce from the sink
turn right move forward turn left move forward turn left go straight turn left towards the countertop bring down the washed sliced lettuce
place the washed sliced lettuce on the countertop
anns.task_desc: Washed sliced lettuce placed on the countertop

high_descs: Walk to countertop across the room.
Pick up the knife on the countertop.
Go to the lettuce on the countertop to your left.
Cut the lettuce on the countertop with the knife.
Move a bit back from the countertop.
Keep the knife behind the potato on the countertop.
Move to the lettuce on the countertop.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the countertop.
Turn left, walk straight past the countertop, turn right, walk straight to the wall, go to the sink to your right and face it.
Put the slice of the lettuce in the sink, wash it and then pick it up.
Go to the wall to your right, turn left, walk past the countertop, turn left, walk straight towards the end of the countertop and then turn to the lettuce on your left.
Put the lettuce on the right side of the knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Wash a slice of lettuce and put it on a countertop.
